Feed NPC corpses to your revenant to gain @@Wsoul points@@N.
Soul points are spent to advance track ranks.

@@WUSAGE@@N
  @@Wrevenant infuse <corpse>@@N

@@WSOUL POINTS GAINED@@N
  Formula: @@W(corpse level - revenant level) / 10@@N

  Corpses weaker than your revenant yield @@Rnothing@@N.
  You must feed corpses at or above your revenant's level.

  Examples (revenant level 100):
    Level  90 corpse = 0 soul points (too weak)
    Level 100 corpse = 0 soul points (no difference)
    Level 110 corpse = 1 soul point
    Level 150 corpse = 5 soul points

@@WSOUL POINT COSTS@@N
  @@WPrimary Track Ranks:@@N
    Rank 1:  Free (starting rank)
    Rank 2:   25 soul points
    Rank 3:   75 soul points
    Rank 4:  150 soul points
    Rank 5:  300 soul points
    Total for max rank: 550 soul points

  @@WSecondary Track Ranks:@@N
    Rank 1:  Free (starting rank)
    Rank 2:   50 soul points
    Rank 3:  150 soul points
    Total for max rank: 200 soul points

  @@WMaximizing both tracks requires 750 total soul points.@@N

@@WTIPS@@N
  - Farm high-level mobs for efficient soul point gain.
  - Use @@Wrevenant rankup@@N to spend accumulated soul points.
  - Use @@Wrevenant status@@N to check your current soul point total.

